    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Prohibits the distribution, sale, or use of single-use plastic food ware containing plastic with regulated perfluoroalkyl and polyfluoroalkyl substances by businesses beginning on 1/1/2028.  Effective 7/1/3000.  (HD2)"
    }
